S.FORM: == Alexis Ajinça == u siwkay niza tatama, nalecuhan i 1988 amihcan 5 a bulad 6 a demiad, Alexis Ajinça, miunduay, mimali i Amilika NBA. u France kanatal a tademaw ciniza. 2008 a mihcan, mapili' nu Siyalothe Sanmaw putiput. ayza sa mimali i Niwauoliang Tihu putiput. kakuniza kalunasulitan-sulu u sulit nu Hulam atu Amilika Alexis Ajinça is a French professional basketball player for the New Orleans Pelicans of the National Basketball Association (NBA). == Alexis Ajinça == o siwkay niza tatama, nalecohan i 1988 amihcan 5 a bolad 6 a demiad, Alexis Ajinça, miondoay, mimali i Amilika NBA. o France kanatal a tademaw ciniza. 2008 a mihcan, mapili' no Siyalothe Sanmaw potipot. ayza sa mimali i Niwaooliang Tiho potipot. kakoniza kalonasolitan-solo o solit no Holam ato Amilika Alexis Ajinça is a French professional basketball player for the New Orleans Pelicans of the National Basketball Association (NBA). He is a 7 ft 2 in (2.18 m), 248 lb (112 kg) center.
